He quotes S1 as evidence of his hypocrisy in requesting evidence when he offers none.
root(ROOT-0, quotes-2)
nsubj(quotes-2, He-1)
dobj(quotes-2, S1-3)
prep_as(quotes-2, evidence-5)
poss(hypocrisy-8, his-7)
